// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-1170 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 059d3697-adbc-5614-a17b-7cea306d2f1b

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*")
